{% set image %}
  {% include "@bolt-components-image/image.twig" with {
    src: "/images/placeholders/landscape-16x9-mountains.jpg",
    alt: "Image alt.",
    attributes: {
      class: "u-bolt-margin-bottom-medium",
    },
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% set fullbutton %}
  <p><bolt-button width="full">button</bolt-button></p>
{% endset %}


{% set paragraph1_unset %}
  {{ image }}
  <p>Item 1. <strong>Do not set <code>valign-items</code> to any values, if the intention is to create equal height layout items</strong>, and each item will push its last child to the bottom.</p>
  {{ fullbutton }}
{% endset %}
{% set paragraph1_other %}
  {{ image }}
  <p>Item 1. <strong>Set <code>valign-items="start | center | end"</code> to create auto height layout items</strong>. Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat molestie vehicula. Sed auctor neque eu tellus rhoncus ut eleifend nibh porttitor. Ut in nulla enim. Phasellus molestie magna non est bibendum non venenatis nisl tempor. Suspendisse dictum feugiat nisl.</p>
  {{ fullbutton }}
{% endset %}
{% set paragraph2 %}
  {{ image }}
  <p>Item 2. This is a short item.</p>
  {{ fullbutton }}
{% endset %}
{% set paragraph3 %}
  {{ image }}
  <p>Item 3. This is a tall item. Phasellus molestie magna non est bibendum non venenatis nisl tempor. Suspendisse dictum feugiat nisl. Ut in nulla enim. Phasellus molestie magna non est bibendum non venenatis nisl tempor. Suspendisse dictum feugiat nisl ut dapibus. Mauris iaculis porttitor posuere. Praesent id metus massa, ut blandit odio. Proin quis tortor orci. Etiam at risus et justo dignissim congue. Donec congue lacinia dui, a porttitor lectus condimentum laoreet. Nunc eu ullamcorper orci. Quisque eget odio ac lectus vestibulum faucibus eget in metus.</p>
  {{ fullbutton }}
{% endset %}
{% set content %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: paragraph1_unset,
  } only %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: paragraph2,
  } only %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: paragraph3,
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout.twig" with {
  gutter: "large",
  row_gutter: "large",
  padding_top: "xlarge",
  padding_bottom: "xlarge",
  template: "tiles@from-small",
  content: content,
  attributes: {
    class: [
      "t-bolt-xdark",
    ]
  },
} only %}
{% set content %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: paragraph1_other,
  } only %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: paragraph2,
  } only %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: paragraph3,
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout.twig" with {
  gutter: "large",
  row_gutter: "large",
  padding_top: "xlarge",
  padding_bottom: "xlarge",
  template: "tiles@from-small",
  valign_items: "start",
  content: content,
  attributes: {
    class: [
      "t-bolt-dark",
    ]
  },
} only %}


{% set media %}
  {% include "@bolt-components-image/image.twig" with {
    src: "/images/placeholders/thumb-square-ivy.jpg",
    alt: "Image alt",
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% set paragraph %}
  {% include "@bolt-components-headline/headline.twig" with {
    text: "Create a flag by setting the template to flag@from-small (or medium). There is a default, but the width can be overwritten with the CSS custom property.",
  } only %}
  <p>Another paragraph. Suspendisse dictum feugiat nisl ut dapibus. Mauris iaculis porttitor posuere. Praesent id metus massa, ut blandit odio. Proin quis tortor orci. Etiam at risus et justo dignissim congue. Donec congue lacinia dui, a porttitor lectus condimentum laoreet. Nunc eu ullamcorper orci. Quisque eget odio ac lectus vestibulum faucibus eget in metus. In pellentesque faucibus vestibulum. Nulla at nulla justo, eget luctus tortor.</p>
{% endset %}
{% set content %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: media,
  } only %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: paragraph,
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout.twig" with {
  padding_top: "large",
  padding_bottom: "large",
  valign_items: "start",
  template: "flag@from-small",
  content: content,
  attributes: {
    style: "--l-bolt-layout-flag-media-width: 200px"
  }
} only %}


{% set itemContent %}
  {% include "@bolt-components-headline/headline.twig" with {
    text: "Special Hero!!!",
    size: "xxxlarge",
  } only %}
  <p>Create a special hero with bleeding image by setting <code>valign-self</code> on layout items. It includes offset options to make a layout item positioned to an edge.</p>
  <p><bolt-button>button</bolt-button></p>
{% endset %}
{% set media %}
  {% include "@bolt-components-image/image.twig" with {
    src: "/images/heros/hero-foreground--indigo.png",
    alt: "Image alt",
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% set content %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: media,
    valign_self: "start-offset",
    order: "last@from-small"
  } only %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: itemContent,
    valign_self: "center",
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout.twig" with {
  gutter: "xlarge",
  padding_top: "large",
  padding_bottom: "large",
  template: "halves@from-small",
  content: content,
  attributes: {
    class: [
      "t-bolt-dark",
    ]
  },
} only %}


{% set media %}
  {% include "@bolt-components-image/image.twig" with {
    src: "/images/heros/hero-foreground--yellow.png",
    alt: "Image alt",
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% set content %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: itemContent,
    valign_self: "center",
  } only %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: media,
    valign_self: "end-offset",
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout.twig" with {
  gutter: "large",
  padding_top: "large",
  padding_bottom: "large",
  template: "halves@from-small 67/33@from-medium",
  content: content,
  attributes: {
    class: [
      "t-bolt-light",
    ]
  },
} only %}


{% set content1 %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: "One layout.",
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% set content2 %}
  {% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout-item.twig" with {
    content: "Stack another layout of the same color and remove extra padding.",
  } only %}
{% endset %}
{% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout.twig" with {
  content: content1,
  attributes: {
    class: [
      "t-bolt-dark",
    ]
  },
} only %}
{% include "@bolt-layouts-layout/layout.twig" with {
  padding_top: "none",
  content: content2,
  attributes: {
    class: [
      "t-bolt-dark",
    ]
  },
} only %}
